{"data":[{"date":"19:54 10/07","title":"V\u1ebb g\u1ee3i c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 xinh \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a hotgirl b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn World Cup Tr\u00e2m Anh","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/ve-goi-cam-va-xinh-dep-cua-hotgirl-binh-luan-world-cup-tram-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u00cdt ai ng\u1edd Tr\u00e2m Anh - hotgirl b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean VTV6 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1eef d\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0129, c\u00f4 \u0111ang c\u00f3 1 c\u1eeda hi\u1ec7u b\u00e1n thu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.</h2>Tr\u00e2m Anh l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c hot girl tham gia b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean VTV6. C\u00f4 c\u00f3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00e1i xoan xinh x\u1eafn v\u00e0 v\u00f2ng 1 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1eb7n, quy\u1ebfn r\u0169. Tr\u00e2m Anh t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ed7 Th\u1ecb Tr\u00e2m Anh sinh n\u0103m 1995. C\u00f4 \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0129 c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u thu\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTr\u00e2m Anh \u0111ang l\u00e0 n\u00e0ng d\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0129 c\u00f3 v\u00f3c d\u00e1ng n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay. Instagram c\u1ee7a c\u00f4 n\u00e0ng c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng ch\u1ee5c ngh\u00ecn ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo d\u00f5i. <br />\r\n<div