 /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4123","checkdouble":"190878"},{"date":"20:30 10/07","title":"M.U m\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00ed Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u th\u0103m s\u00e2n Old Trafford","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/mu-moi-doi-bong-nhi-thai-lan-vua-duoc-giai-cuu-tham-san-old-trafford.JPG","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4122","checkdouble":"190880"},{"date":"06:40 11/07","title":"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba chia s\u1ebb chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00ed v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/tien-ve-pogba-chia-se-chien-thang-truoc-bi-cung-doi-bong-nhi-vua-duoc-giai-cuu.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0102n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup nh\u01b0ng Pogba v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean chia s\u1ebb ni\u1ec1m vui v\u1edbi c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua gi\u1edd ph\u00fat sinh t\u1eed \u1edf h\u00e0ng Tham Luang, Th\u00e1i Lan.</h2>Paul Pogba v\u1eeba c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \"ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh em\" B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. T\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o top 2 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean chia s\u1ebb ni\u1ec1m vui v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00ed v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u sau 17 ng\u00e0y k\u1eb9t trong hang Tham Luang, Th\u00e1i Lan.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Capture_1.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\"Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, vinh quang d\u00e0nh cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh h\u00f9ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1. L\u00e0m t\u1ed1t l\u1eafm, c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai\", Pogba chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u00f9ng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh 12 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mang t\u00ean \"L\u1ee3n r\u1eebng\" \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi quan t\u00e2m trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, FIFA \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi m\u1eddi th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u00e1i Lan tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 15/7 nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00f4m qua (10/7), l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee9u h\u1ed9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebft c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean kh\u1ecfi hang Tham Luang. Sau \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c em \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng 12 \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 sang Nga l\u00e0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4121","checkdouble":"190908"},{"date":"22:19 10/07","title":"David Trezeguet n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/10/david-trezeguet-noi-gi-ve-thuong-vu-ronaldo-toi-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>David Trezeguet ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Juventus, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A chi \u0111\u1eadm mua si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo s\u1eafp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juventus</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo. Sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Trezeguet ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Juventus v\u1ec1 Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"David Trezeguet ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Juventus v\u1ec1 Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/David-Trezeguet-phat-bieu-ve-Juventus-ve-Ronaldo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn t\u1edbi Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/vu-ronaldo-den-juventus-coi-nhu-da-xong-180-190882.html\" target=\"_blank\">Juventus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Ronaldo</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, CR7 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Higuain \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Juventus.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRonaldo s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus, m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a anh b\u1ecf t\u00fai 30 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin. D\u00f9 33 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng CR7 v\u1eabn duy tr\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u sao M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Juventus t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Serie A m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1ng xem h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Trezeguet \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao vi\u1ec7c Juventus k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Trezeguet ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Juventus, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A chi \u0111\u1eadm mua si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo toi Juventus\" title=\"Ronaldo toi Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Emre-Can-hao-huc-truoc-vien-canh-Ronaldo-gia-nhap-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Trezeguet tin\u00a0</span>Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng theo d\u00f5i ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Juventus. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m cho Juventus, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cRonaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho Juventus. C\u00f2n qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i li\u1ec7u Ronaldo c\u00f3 gi\u00fap Juventus gi\u00e0nh Champions League hay kh\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u1ed1t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cLi\u1ec7u Gonzalo Higuain c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Ronaldo hay kh\u00f4ng \u01b0? T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a CLB. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nhau\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4120","checkdouble":"190885"},{"date":"20:31 10/07","title":"Mbappe c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi PSG v\u00ec l\u00fd do n\u00e0y?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/10/20/mbappe-co-the-roi-psg-vi-ly-do-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kylian Mbappe r\u1eddi PSG trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c quy\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng \u1edf PSG.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01b0ng chi\u1ec1u qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c \u1edf PSG</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2017, PSG \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi chi t\u1edbi 222 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar t\u1eeb Barca. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 c\u00fa s\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. V\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 cao k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kylian Mbappe r\u1eddi PSG v\u00ec m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kylian Mbappe r\u1eddi PSG v\u00ec m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/17/Kylian-Mbappe-roi-PSG-vi-mau-thuan-voi-Neymar-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG c\u01b0ng chi\u1ec1u Neymar qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed Neymar l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u01b0ng chi\u1ec1u. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Neymar l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u01b0\u1edbp quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t 11m c\u1ee7a Edison Cavani, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u1edf nh\u1eefng c\u1ef1 l\u00fd \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Uruguay th\u00ec Neymar c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Neymar khi\u1ebfn n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a PSG xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn, HLV Unai Emery khi c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u00f4ng c\u00f2n cho h\u1ecd t\u1ef1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng quy\u1ec1n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mbappe c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Neymar</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kylian Mbappe r\u1eddi PSG trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c quy\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng \u1edf PSG.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe khong hai long voi Neymar\" title=\"Mbappe kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Neymar\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/mbappe.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mbappe kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Neymar</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Cavani m\u00e0 Mbappe c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c BL\u0110 PSG qu\u00e1 \u01b0u \u00e1i ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Ph\u00e1p c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ngay c\u1ea3 khi Mbappe v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga anh v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 PSG \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao cho Neymar.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Hi\u1ec7n Real, Barca v\u00e0 MU \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998, song s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 230 tri\u1ec7u euro l\u00e0 r\u00e0o c\u1ea3n l\u1edbn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/buffon-that-bai-tai-world-cup-2018-se-giup-neymar-manh-me-hon-421-190835.html\" target=\"_blank\">Buffon \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 Neymar</span>, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Juventus tin si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4119","checkdouble":"190876"},{"date":"18:45 10/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 10/07: MU \u0111i n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1edd quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1ee5 sao 100 tri\u1ec7u euro","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/10/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-1007-mu-di-nuoc-co-quan-trong-vu-sao-100-trieu-euro.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 10/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU \u0111i n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1edd quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1ee5 sao 100 tri\u1ec7u euro</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 1007 MU \u0111i n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1edd quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1ee5 Savic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 1007 MU \u0111i n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1edd quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1ee5 Savic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/16/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-1007-MU-di-nuoc-co-quan-trong-vu-Savic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1edbi Italia \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1ee5 Milinkovic-Savic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, MU \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi sang Italia \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 v\u00e0 trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c quan ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Lazio \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Walker: &ldquo;B\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed gia \u0111\u00ecnh gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh bay cao&rdquo;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kyle Walker ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh sau khi l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed gia \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap cho Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Wenger b\u1eadt b\u00e3i kh\u1ecfi Arsenal v\u00ec...Kante?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsene Wenger r\u1eddi Arsenal v\u00ec N'Golo Kante, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p Gilles Favard, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng l\u00e0m c\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n cho Nantes v\u00e0 Bordeaux.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Eden Hazard t\u1edbi La Liga nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Real?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca muon mua Eden Hazard\" title=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Barca-muon-mua-Eden-Hazard-voi-gia-100-trieu-euro-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Real Madrid trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00e2y! Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Croatia v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Croatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 s\u1eedng s\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u0110\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Filip Tapalovic c\u0169ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c&nbsp;n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Rooney ch\u00fac \u0111\u00e0n em v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Wayne Rooney v\u1eeba m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i DC United. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Rooney l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u00fac Tam s\u01b0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Real cho Hazard</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mua Eden Hazard nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eeba b\u1ecb Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>&quot;MU c\u1ea7n ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi Mourinho&quot;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mark Bosnich ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf khuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford n\u00ean ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Lindelof ch\u01a1i \u1edf \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lindelof vs Thuy Si\" title=\"Lindelof vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/vi-sao-lindelof-choi-o-dt-thuy-dien-tot-hon-o-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rio Ferdinand n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Lindelof</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Rio Ferdinand ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Victor Lindelof, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef1 s\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng t\u1eeb NHM l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4118","checkdouble":"190873"},{"date":"21:29 10/07","title":"V\u1ee5 Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 xong!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/CHINH-THUC-Cristiano-Ronaldo-toi-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 xong, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 bay \u0111\u1ebfn Hy L\u1ea1p \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Juventus</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C1 2018 v\u1edbi Liverpool, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus \u0111\u00e3 xong h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus \u0111\u00e3 xong h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/vu-ronaldo-den-juventus-coi-nhu-da-xong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn t\u1edbi Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CR7 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Real, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Jorge Mendes c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3. M\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p k\u00edn gi\u1eefa Jorge Mendes v\u00e0 quan ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u1edf Anh, hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Ronaldo s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus, m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a anh s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Real \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n CR7 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Gonzalo Higuain t\u1eeb Napoli (90 tri\u1ec7u euro) \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 xong, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 bay \u0111\u1ebfn Hy L\u1ea1p \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo toi Juventus\" title=\"Ronaldo toi Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Emre-Can-hao-huc-truoc-vien-canh-Ronaldo-gia-nhap-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Juventus, Andrea Agnelli, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang bay t\u1eeb Pisa \u0111\u1ebfn Kalamata, n\u01a1i Ronaldo \u0111ang \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 sau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup c\u00f9ng \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. \u00d4ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p CR7 v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1t n\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/lo-so-ao-cua-ronaldo-o-juventus-180-190540.html\" target=\"_blank\">s\u1ed1 \u00e1o c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u1edf Juventus</span> c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo \u0111\u00f3 anh s\u1ebd m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Gonzalo Higuain kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u1edf Juvetus, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina mu\u1ed1n s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh v\u1edbi CR7 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&quot;Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi n\u1ebfu Ronaldo ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Higuain. H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft nhau r\u1ea5t r\u00f5, khi h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i kho\u1ea3ng 80 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi nhau. N\u1ebfu Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, s\u1ebd th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c.&quot;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4117","checkdouble":"190882"},{"date":"22:59 10/07","title":"Real nh\u1eafm sao kh\u1ee7ng MU thay Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/12/real-nham-sao-khung-mu-thay-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mua Romelu Lukaku t\u1eeb MU n\u1ebfu Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Don Balon c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real s\u1eafp m\u1ea5t Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Juventus. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 bay \u0111\u1ebfn Hy L\u1ea1p, n\u01a1i Ronaldo \u0111ang ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mua Romelu Lukaku thay Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mua Romelu Lukaku thay Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Real-Madrid-mua-Romelu-Lukaku-thay-Cristiano-Ronaldo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 CR7 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng\u00a0 gi\u1eefa c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed phanh phui.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Ronaldo s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia anh s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1edbi 30 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a. \u0110\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d ph\u1ea3i chi t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean Ronaldo s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Juventus, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Gonzalo Higuain \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Napoli (90 tri\u1ec7u euro).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/vu-ronaldo-den-juventus-coi-nhu-da-xong-180-190882.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span> \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real mu\u1ed1n mua Lukaku</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mua Romelu Lukaku t\u1eeb MU n\u1ebfu Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Don Balon c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lukaku\" title=\"Lukaku\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Jose-Mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-Romelu-Lukaku-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n mua Lukaku thay Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Lukaku, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993.\u00a0Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 M.U ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb Everton.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed Real c\u00f2n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u00f9ng Karim Benzema ho\u1eb7c Mateo Kovacic \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford nh\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Real l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Lukaku l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1edf M.U, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4116","checkdouble":"190887"},{"date":"23:04 10/07","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Real x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Ronaldo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/chinh-thuc-real-xac-nhan-ronaldo-cap-ben-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 118 tri\u1ec7u euro (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 105 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Ronaldo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Real, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. Juventus \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda CR7.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/CHINH-THUC-Cristiano-Ronaldo-toi-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Ronaldo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00f4m nay, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Juventus, Andrea Agnelli \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1eeb Pisa \u0111\u1ebfn Hy L\u1ea1p, n\u01a1i Ronaldo \u0111ang ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus: &ldquo;Real Madrid CF x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juventus k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u00fang c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi&quot;.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Real mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1edbi Ronaldo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Real, Ronaldo s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi Real x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Los Blancos, Sergio Ramos \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t CR7: &ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd nh\u1edb v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng nhau c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Anh s\u1ebd m\u00e3i kh\u1eafc ghi v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Ch\u00fac Ronaldo g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u may m\u1eafn \u1edf CLB m\u1edbi&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2009, trong su\u1ed1t 9 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Santiago Bernabeu, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 15 danh hi\u1ec7u, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 2 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga, 2 C\u00fap nh\u00e0 Vua T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 4 danh hi\u1ec7u Champions League.</p>\r\n<h2>Chi ti\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Ronaldo k\u00fd v\u1edbi Juventus<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a ra chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd v\u1edbi Juventus, song gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/chinh-thuc-real-xac-nhan-ronaldo-cap-ben-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Theo Sky Sports, Juventus ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 105 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd b\u1ecf t\u00fai 30 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a. Theo Sky Sports, Real Madrid s\u1ebd thu v\u1ec1 118 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 105 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng).<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, Guardian th\u00ec kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Juventus ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 100 tri\u1ec7u euro) \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo. Ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Guardian c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft Real ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 340 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu CR7 (bao g\u1ed3m 100 tri\u1ec7u euro ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, 240 tri\u1ec7u ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 thu\u1ebf).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Gonzalo Higuain \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Juventus. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0&rdquo; ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 90 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina t\u1eeb Napoli.</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Serie A m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1ng xem h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1985 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Juventus v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/lo-so-ao-cua-ronaldo-o-juventus-180-190540.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 \u1edf Juventus</span>, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o do Juan Cuadrado m\u1eb7c \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 cho Ronaldo v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 16 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4115","checkdouble":"190888"},{"date":"00:17 11/07","title":"Cristiano Ronaldo g\u1eedi t\u00e2m th\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea7y x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cristiano Ronaldo vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 g\u1eedi Real Madrid, t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf t\u00ecnh y\u00eau r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e2m th\u01b0 \u0111\u1eabm n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-real-xac-nhan-ronaldo-cap-ben-juventus-180-190888.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Juventus</span>. Theo Sky Sports, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1985 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin, h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a. Real thu v\u1ec1 118 tri\u1ec7u euro (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 105 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 g\u1eedi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 g\u1eedi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo g\u1eedi t\u00e2m th\u01b0 \u0111\u1eabm n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft chia tay Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 g\u1eedi Real Madrid, t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf t\u00ecnh y\u00eau r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o qu\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Real Madrid, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac nh\u1ea5t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh bi\u1ebft \u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3m \u01a1n NHM \u0111\u00e3 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 t\u00f4i trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao t\u00f4i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd hi\u1ec3u cho quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. 9 n\u0103m qua th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7y cay \u0111\u1eafng. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd qu\u00ean qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Real Madrid&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ng\u00e0y t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n n\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb NHM, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u1edf Real v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng HLV gi\u1ecfi. 4 Champions League, 4 Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng v\u00e0 3 gi\u00e0y V\u00e0ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong th\u1eddi gian kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real. M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>H\u1ecd ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, Sergio Ramos \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t CR7: &ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd nh\u1edb v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng nhau c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Anh s\u1ebd m\u00e3i kh\u1eafc ghi v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Ch\u00fac Ronaldo g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u may m\u1eafn \u1edf CLB m\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSami Khedira, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u1edf Real v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho Juventus kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi b\u00ean nhau \u1edf Real, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh anh \u1ea5y m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. H\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh cho fan Juventus&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dybala len tieng moi chao Ronaldo\" title=\"Dybala l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng m\u1eddi ch\u00e0o Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/dybala.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Dybala l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPaulo Dybala&rlm; th\u00ec chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mong \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f9ng Ronaldo thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4114","checkdouble":"190889"},{"date":"20:49 10/07","title":"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Andre Gomes?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/thuc-hu-vu-arsenal-chi-35-trieu-euro-mua-andre-gomes.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal mua Andre Gomes l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, HLV Unai Emery kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n quan t\u00e2m Andre Gomes</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Leno, trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Stephan Lichtsteiner.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ee5 Arsenal mua Andre Gomes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ee5 Arsenal mua Andre Gomes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/14/HLV-Unai-Emery-len-tieng-vu-Arsenal-mua-Andre-Gomes-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n quan t\u00e2m Andre Gomes</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi 30 tri\u1ec7u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Vi\u1ec7c Jack Wilshere ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn West Ham bu\u1ed9c c\u1ef1u HLV c\u1ee7a PSG ph\u1ea3i n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Mirror, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-barca-172-190353.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Andre Gomes</span> c\u1ee7a Barca. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Arsenal s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1ee7 35 tri\u1ec7u euro, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f3a s\u1ed5 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn quan t\u00e2m Andre Gomes</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal mua Andre Gomes l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, HLV Unai Emery kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal phu nhan quan tam Andre Gomes\" title=\"Arsenal ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn quan t\u00e2m Andre Gomes\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/thuc-hu-vu-arsenal-chi-35-trieu-euro-mua-andre-gomes.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn quan t\u00e2m Andre Gomes</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m nh\u01b0 Gomes, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eadyTottenham v\u00e0 West Ham s\u1ebd c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m Lucas Torreira c\u1ee7a Sampdoria v\u00e0 Steven Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla, v\u1edbi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p mua m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd mua Torreira.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Anh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal. Torreira v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Uruguay. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap HLV Emery c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4113","checkdouble":"190877"},{"date":"21:44 10/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! Danh s\u00e1ch 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/day-danh-sach-2-cau-thu-ma-hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-giu-bang-duoc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Maurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Willian, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay Conte tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y 15/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Hazard v\u00e0 Willian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay th\u1ebf Conte ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Chelsea. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn ch\u1ee9c nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Hi\u1ec7n c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u00ean BL\u0110 The Blues k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua b\u00e1n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri muon chuyen nhuong Chelsea 2018 giu chan Hazard va Willian\" title=\"HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Hazard v\u00e0 Willian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/day-danh-sach-2-cau-thu-ma-hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-giu-bang-duoc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Hazard v\u00e0 Willian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Mundo Deportivo, Maurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Willian, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n The Blues gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-khong-ban-willian-cho-barca-172-189958.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho M.U. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f2n v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Hazard, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sau World Cup 2018. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111ang nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i Los Blancos.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i theo \u00fd c\u1ee7a Sarri, h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa hai b\u00ean c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020. \u0110\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho Hazard m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 400.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y 15/07</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00f4m nay, HLV Conte v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e8 2018. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9 sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, HLV Conte xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maurizio Sarri\" title=\"Maurizio Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/hlv-sarri-se-thay-doi-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Maurizio Sarri s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay Conte</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, Chelsea v\u1eabn \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c bu\u1ed9c Conte ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c, h\u1ecd l\u1ea5y l\u00fd do kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League \u0111\u1ec3 bu\u1ed9c \u00f4ng n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Conte quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u00e1m tr\u1ee5 \u1edf Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong 5 ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi n\u1ebfu Conte v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 th\u00f4i vi\u1ec7c Chelsea s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n sa th\u1ea3i v\u00e0 b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n. HLV Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea chi 6 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Napoli \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang th\u00fac \u00e9p Chelsea gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nhanh chuy\u1ec7n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Conte \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m m\u00ecnh. HLV Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi The Blues, nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng trung b\u00ecnh 5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4112","checkdouble":"190884"},{"date":"21:50 10/07","title":"Arsenal CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 4 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/arsenal-chinh-thuc-xac-nhan-co-tan-binh-thu-4-tri-gia-30-trieu-euro.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal mua Lucas Torreira t\u1eeb Sampdoria th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Torreira</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Arsenal \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Lucas Torreira t\u1eeb Sampdoria. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Jack Wilshere \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Arsenal mua Lucas Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Arsenal mua Lucas Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/arsenal-chinh-thuc-xac-nhan-co-tan-binh-thu-4-tri-gia-30-trieu-euro.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lucas Torreira t\u1edbi Arsenal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c ra Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 6, song th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng qua b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 sau World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLucas Torreira v\u00e0 Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018, h\u1ecd d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. Ngay khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/torreira-sap-toi-arsenal-kiem-tra-y-te-172-190746.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mua Lucas Torreira</span> t\u1eeb Sampdoria th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Sampdoria nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTorreira l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, sau Sokratis, Bernd Leno v\u00e0 Stephan Lichtsteiner. Ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Arsenal v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 120.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf s\u00e2n Emirates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Emery \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Torreira</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Torreira, HLV Unai Emery s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery danh gia cao Lucas Torreira\" title=\"HLV Emery \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Lucas Torreira\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/gu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Lucas Torreira</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Lucas Torreira l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vinh d\u1ef1 khi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. \u0110\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 xem m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf 2 m\u00f9a g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Sampdoria, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eeba ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Torreira \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal v\u00e0 mong c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi CLB&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div>V\u1edbi Torreira anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Arsenal li\u00ean h\u1ec7. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00e0 \u1edf c\u1ea3 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u n\u1eefa, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Arsenal&rdquo;.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Sampdoria, Torreira ra s\u00e2n 74 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111eo b\u00e1m d\u1ebbo dai.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ed1t, anh ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4111","checkdouble":"190886"}]}